etymology.description: semantic: 囗(囗) (wéi, "enclosure") + phonetic: 君(君) (jūn, "sovereign") = grain storage enclosed within a structure
etymology.interpretation: The character 囷(jùn) illustrates the idea of storing grains by combining the semantic element 囗(囗) (wéi, "enclosure") representing a structure and the phonetic element 君(君) (jūn, "sovereign") to suggest pronunciation.
